      </div>
      <div class="d-flex flex-column">
        <label for="type" class="align-middle text-light pr-2">What type of programmer are you?</label>
        <textarea name="type" id="type" cols="30" rows="4" placeholder="i.e. Web Developer, Data Scientist, etc...">{{user.survey.type}}</textarea>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="worker" class="align-middle text-light pr-2">How would you describe your work ethic?</label>
        <select class="custom-select" id="worker">
          <option selected>{{user.survey.worker}}</option>
          <option>Work and energy drinks all night, everynight</option>
          <option>Hard worker but I need my social life balance</option>
          <option>Do bare minimum to get the work done and then do other hobbies</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="ideal_date" class="align-middle text-light pr-2">What is your ideal date night?</label>
        <select class="custom-select" id="ideal_date">
          <option selected>{{user.survey.ideal_date}}</option>
          <option>Stay in, get takeout, watch a movie or play video games</option>
          <option>Go out to a nice restaurant or picnic and stare into each otherâ€™s eyes</option>
          <option>Go out with a group of friends for a game night or drinks</option>
          <option>Hit the club, take some shots, initiate the bender</option>
        </select>
